{"tid":1131941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"就台灣提出遣送疑犯要求　林鄭月娥：不存在石沉大海","createTime":"2019-04-30T03:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T10:31:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"724b8de10c109d2b0deff14de3827f4a967ae5dd","tid":1131941,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:28:57.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥指出，就台灣當局提出遣送疑犯回台灣受審的要求，不存在石沉大海，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為之前未有實質法律基礎及方向</span>以回應台灣當局，但現時有條件與台灣磋商，將透過協進會與策進會的平台處理。她表示，保安局局長<span style=\"color: red;\">將於這兩天</span>正式回信展開工作，但表示雙方的討論不會公開，會達致一定成果才交代。<br />\n<br />\n她又表示，一直有與受害人家屬保持聯絡，包括親自寫信，亦有親自閱讀受害人家屬的來信及電郵。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政府已於2月12日向家屬提供實質回應，表示已有法律基礎</span>，可按台灣當局的要求遣送疑犯回台灣接受法律制裁。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1455264-20190430.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1455264-20190430.htm&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYuaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=720554b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1455264-20190430.htm&h=b489c210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1455264-20190430.htm</a>"},{"pid":"029e2a4e8a3cd3b962b2ce09879ff8e52e731269","tid":1131941,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:31:50.000Z","msg":"拖糧三個月都可以話係行規嚟啦，邊撚度有石沉大海啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b41524e579d50b92c174a3dfd3850d0f519ac8","tid":1131941,"uid":33668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:01:31.000Z","msg":"5毛繼續用拖糧轉移視線"},{"pid":"e85cf50fb60904da51c11c9291f677a8844db17c","tid":1131941,"uid":15647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"91b41524e579d50b92c174a3dfd3850d0f519ac8","tid":1131941,"uid":33668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:01:31.000Z","msg":"5毛繼續用拖糧轉移視線"},"citedBy":